Path: https://objects.eodc.eu:443/e05ab01a9d56408d82ac32d69a5aae2a:202604-s02msil2a-eu/06/products/cpm_v270/S2C_MSIL2A_20260406T135731_N0512_R010_T27WVV_20260406T173512.zarr/measurements/reflectance/r20m/b02
Shape: 5490 x 5490
